    <p>Jekyll is the SSG built into GitHub, covered on the following pages:</p>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="/jamstack/github-pages-starter-pack/">Github Pages Starter Pack</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://help.github.com/en/articles/using-a-static-site-generator-other-than-jekyll">Using A Static Site Generator other than Jekyll</a></li>
    </ul>

